Pizza Funghi

For the pizza dough:

500 grams all-purpose flour
8 grams instant or active dry yeast
7 grams sea salt
338 grams warm water
13 grams olive oil
Semolina flour or cornmeal

For the sauce and toppings:

180 gr sliced mixed mushrooms
1 tablespoon each finely chopped fresh thyme and oregano, plus more sprigs for topping
sea salt, to taste
1 tablespoon olive oil
fresh lemon juice
100 gr goat cheese, crumbled
50 gr shredded mozzarella cheese
finely chopped chives
